Fast command-line image viewer
-----------------------------

This app is an alternative for qiv on linux.

GOALS: - sorted by priority
------

* display image as fast as possible
   - decode images on separated thread(s)
   - cache decoded images in mem/disk

 * control from command-line

 * eliminate need of moving hands from keyboard to mouse and back

 * fast image tagging - recognize same images by checksums

 * organize images

 * view/download images on www page

 * open images from menu (but who want's this? :-))

IMPLEMENTED:
------------
   - cache decoded images in mem
   - prepare images on separated thread
   - control from command-line
   - rotate image
   - index image by its sha1 sum
